events.name: Google Cloud Study Jam 2019 - GCDC Coimbatore
events.description:
Speakers:

1. Fahid M (GCP / Kubernetes Introduction)
2. Praveen Thirumurugan (GCP Walk-through)

About the Event:

Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin? Join us for our Cloud Study Jam!

Get official Google training, a $55+ value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with the Cloud Console, Kubernetes, Security, IoT on Cloud, and Machine Learning.

Then after our live session, you will have free access to more labs you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to compete in any labs you want.

Bring a laptop and charger (PC, Mac or Chromebook)! The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers. For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Firefox or Chrome installed. Don’t forget your charger.

Google Cloud Platform, offered by Google, is a suite of cloud computing services that run on the same infrastructure that Google uses internally for its end-user products, such as Google Search and YouTube.

events.name: Google Cloud Next '19 Extended Coimbatore
events.description:
Build out your technical expertise while getting a behind-the-scenes look at the latest Google Cloud innovations. Hear from customers on how they’re extending the value of the cloud. Explore the latest business trends and emerging technologies through immersive learning experiences.

GCDC Coimbatore will be hosting a two-hour session with a guest speaker. The quick sessions include,

4 to 4:30 - Guest Speaker Keynote
4:30 to 4:45 - Snacks / Community Breakout
4:45 to 6 - Google Cloud Next '19 Keynote

events.name: GDG Cloud Coimbatore - Monthly Learning Webinar Series
events.description:
Want to get started on the Google Cloud, but don't know where to begin? Join us online* every month on the 3rd week for an rewarding** webinar and learn about Google Cloud!

Every Monthly Learning Webinar is scheduled for 1 hour and one concept or a lab will be aired to the audience. You're welcome to send your needs/concepts that you need to learn.

Agenda:

8:00 to 9:00 pm: Webinar of 1 topic in Google Cloud.
9:00 to 9:15 pm: QA regarding Community Queries.
______________________________________________________

* Visit us at https://youtu.be/OSqKXHx1GNc to watch the webinar. Until the website is open for the community, Hangouts Meet link will be shared 1 day in advance for those who have completed the RSVP.

** E-Certificates will be provided for all participants for events conducted by GDG Cloud Coimbatore going forward.

Hacktoberfest® is open to everyone in our global community.
